org.hyperic.hq.hqapi1
Class ApplicationApi

java.lang.Object
  org.hyperic.hq.hqapi1.ApplicationApi

public class ApplicationApi
extends java.lang.Object

The Hyperic HQ Application API.

This class provides access to the applications within the HQ system. Each of the methods in this class return response objects that wrap the result of the method with a ResponseStatus and a ServiceError that indicates the error if the response status is ResponseStatus.FAILURE.
